    "body": "Just bumped into this error while attempting to deploy this [`ERC20GodMode`](https://github.com/PaulRBerg/prb-contracts/blob/878032e1925f5366e52ce7a93bb6a12c9a4098e4/src/token/erc20/ERC20GodMode.sol) contract with Ledger:\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nforge create src/token/erc20/ERC20GodMode.sol:ERC20GodMode \\\r\n--ledger \\\r\n--rpc-url \"localhost\" \\\r\n--constructor-args \\\r\n\"Test token\" \\\r\n\"TKN\" \\\r\n18\r\n```\r\n\r\nRunning the command without the `--ledger` flag works.\r\n\r\nError:\r\n\r\n> (code: -32000, message: intrinsic gas too high, data: None)",
